title_bed_bats_review: Serviced apartment in Dhaka · ★New · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 1 bath
listing_description:
Welcome to our fully furnished 350 sq. ft studio apartment!

Our building consists of an array of amenities:
* Swimming pool
* Multi-purpose hall with stage
* Movie theatre (50 seats)
* Prayer room
* Fully equipped Gym
* Steam room
* Rooftop BBQ station
* Jogging track and rooftop gardens with seating
* Lounge area
* 24/7 Security

We also provide services:
* Room and bathroom cleaning
* Laundry Services
* Garbage collection
* Food (menu will be provided) 
* Airport drop off and Pick up
